# Clawd Grok — Project Overview

**Clawd Grok** (`clawd-grok`) is the world's first Grok-powered Solana perpetual futures CLI agent. Terminal-native, keyboard-driven, and built for traders who live in the command line. Combines **xAI Grok reasoning** with **Phoenix DEX perps** via Vulcan execution.

## Tech Stack

- **Language**: TypeScript (ES2022, ESNext modules)
- **Runtime**: Bun (primary)
- **AI Brain**: xAI Grok (grok-4.3, grok-4.20, grok-3-mini) via OpenAI-compatible Chat Completions API
- **UI Framework**: React with [OpenTUI](https://github.com/anomalyco/opentui) for terminal rendering
- **Build**: `tsc` (TypeScript compiler)
- **Package Manager**: Bun
- **API Client**: OpenAI SDK (for OpenAI-compatible xAI API)
- **Tools**: Bash-only (all file operations via shell commands)
- **Search**: X Search API + Web Search via xAI Responses API
- **Blockchain**: Solana (Phoenix DEX perpetuals, Vulcan execution)
- **Storage**: SQLite (sessions, transcripts, tool results, usage tracking)

